<p>
  The details of Hồ Chí Minh's life before he came to power in Vietnam are uncertain. He is known to have used between 50[10]: 582  and 200 pseudonyms.[11]
  Information on his birth and early life is ambiguous and subject to academic debate.
  At least four existing official biographies vary on names, dates, places, and other hard
